1000个移动字符:


1000个撤销字符:


1000个重做字符:




#include <time.h>
#include<list>
int main(void)
{
	clock_t ts, te;

	puts("MY_LIST:");
	List<long> lst;

	ts = clock();
	for (long i = 0; i < 10000000; ++i)
	{
		lst.InsertTail(114514);
	}
	te = clock();
	printf("插入耗时:%ldms\n", te - ts);

	ts = clock();
	lst.RemoveAll();
	te = clock();
	printf("释放耗时:%ldms\n", te - ts);

	puts("STD_LIST:");
	std::list<long> stdlst;

	ts = clock();
	for (long i = 0; i < 10000000; ++i)
	{
		stdlst.push_back(114514);
	}
	te = clock();
	printf("插入耗时:%ldms\n", te - ts);

	ts = clock();
	stdlst.clear();
	te = clock();
	printf("释放耗时:%ldms\n", te - ts);

	return -1;
}
